{"tid":1281471,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[夢遊online]基本備戰指南（文宣、物資、網絡消息篇）","createTime":"2019-07-03T09:49:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T15:26:13.000Z","uid":187796,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"088037331534886f12cf10b5a0c211450c21882e","tid":1281471,"uid":187796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T09:49:07.000Z","msg":"應該會有好多人tldr<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />整個簡單目錄<br />\n目錄：<br />\n1. 文宣篇<br />\n2. 物資篇（簡單版）<br />\n3. tg網絡消息篇（極基本版）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">[文宣篇]</span><br />\n**唔係香港嘅隊友，唔知自已可以做咩嘅隊友，係你地嘅機會啦！文宣唔係淨係上到場嘅人先有資格share，唔好怕醜，多你一個好多！你仲可以幫手翻譯比國外嘅朋友仔聽！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n**文宣嘅要點：<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">「Share出去，然後叫人Share出去」</span></span>，單單Share出去影響力唔夠大，做多一步叫人Share出去，就可以滾雪球滾好快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，係social media到洗一波版<br />\n而家興論戰開打，事實上，政府嘅意圖好明顯，就係<span style=\"color: red;\">將71個focus shift落去「暴力行為」到</span>，而配合主流媒體，令大眾嘅目光投放係「可見嘅行為」上，而<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">忽略左前線冒住性命危險同法律風險表達嘅訴求</span></span>。<br />\n所以，我地現階段打興論戰最重要嘅一點，係要<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">將焦點變番做我地一直以黎嘅訴求</span></span>！<br />\n<br />\n護航型文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：<br />\n1.100萬人遊行，試過；200萬+1人遊行，試過；集會，試過；包圍，試過；甚至有人死諫，政府提都冇提，今次係試盡所有所謂非暴力之後嘅方法，<span style=\"color: red;\">你可以唔認同佢地做法，但要聆聽佢地嘅聲音</span><br />\n2.有部分外國人認為我地陷入分裂，請幫手澄清！<br />\n<br />\n攻擊型文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：<br />\n1.放大啲狗嘅<span style=\"color: red;\">出醜事件</span>，特別係圍狗總個次，同埋戴錶5點出事個次，表明政府係製造恐慌、亂局後扮正氣出黎指責<br />\n2.狗拒絕讓路比救護車，盡展<span style=\"color: red;\">人性光輝</span><br />\n3.政府迴避訴求，將焦點放係衝擊行為而<span style=\"color: red;\">冇提過背後嘅訴求</span><br />\n<br />\n增幅型文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：<br />\n1.所有你覺得<span style=\"color: gold;\">窩心</span>嘅野，Share出去，呢份窩心係我地對抗絕望嘅最大武器（一齊走 一齊走 一齊走<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n2.如果有明確嘅Action，Share出去就啱，文宣對人數好重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">[物資篇（簡單版）]</span><br />\n**係夢遊online入面，話知你係補師定坦都好，裝備都係極之重要<br />\n**今次物資明顯比612好好多，裝備好左，前線嘅信心同戰力都大啲，唔會輕易被擊退（但真係要特別感謝前線，即使有裝備，留係前線亦唔簡單）<br />\n**[未fact check] 好似有狗已經開始搵cctv，所以大家買野個陣都需要小心<br />\n**出唔到黎嘅人都可以幫手出錢比身邊嘅人買物資，我諗唔少學生都開始買到窮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另外<span style=\"color: red;\">強烈建議大家準備好自己嘅物資</span>，保護自己同時減輕物資站負擔，強烈建議自己配備：<br />\n1.純色黑衫（唔好有logo）<br />\n2.口罩(N95/黑色口罩/普通口罩，N95五金鋪有，黑口罩藥房有)<br />\n3.毛巾<br />\n4.水，乾糧，寶礦力，得力素等<br />\n5.帽<br />\n6.唔係黑色嘅衫，除時更換<br />\n7.散銀，取代八達通<br />\n8.極重要：哮喘病人記得帶哮喘藥，其他人都要帶自己需要嘅藥物<br />\n9.長遮(落雨同出太陽要帶遮)<br />\n<br />\n相對optional，但建議要自己帶：<br />\n1.手套（搬野冇咁傷手，亦唔會留指紋）<br />\n2.頭盔（上前必備）<br />\n3.尿袋（冇電睇唔到消息，必要時又拍唔到片）<br />\n4.眼罩(3M，可以cup實對眼個隻，五金鋪有)<br />\n5.較剪（放入筆袋，唔係好難姐）<br />\n6.退熱貼<br />\n7.索帶<br />\n<br />\n想補補裝嘅朋友可以參考其他巴打寫嘅：<br />\n[齊齊升Level] 野餐裝備整合篇<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1281138\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1281138</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">[網絡消息篇（極簡單版，純屬個人理解，如果有人有心得隨時開post補上）]</span><br />\n**消息好重要，係判斷形勢、思考策略嘅基礎，所以絕對要跟貼啲即時資訊<br />\n**subscribe channel係唔會令狗睇到你個tg account，可以安心subscribe <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/scottscout\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fscottscout&d=Cxq6fU51OcuVLB8gp8NaV%2B2wegjmRFMzjbv%2B285MJ7g%3D&h=aec45690\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/scottscout</a><br />\n必入，由哨兵組成嘅channel，行動個陣會有大量現場資訊（e.g. 0910 中環海濱7號碼頭巡緊，5隻），方便了解敵人部署同判斷撤退路線<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/antiextraditionverifiednews\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fantiextraditionverifiednews&d=Cxq6fU51OcuVLB8gp8NaV%2B2wegjmRFMzjbv%2B285MJ7g%3D&h=6d24fcb4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/antiextraditionverifiednews</a><br />\n必入，資訊準確，即時現場消息多，但冇哨兵果個咁多，入呢個會有重要資訊（e.g. 出咩旗，前線狀況），但唔會有大量敵人分佈嘅消息<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/bignewsmaterial\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fbignewsmaterial&d=Cxq6fU51OcuVLB8gp8NaV%2B2wegjmRFMzjbv%2B285MJ7g%3D&h=8c99c85d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/bignewsmaterial</a><br />\n可入可不入，呢個物資組開，多物資消息，但主要消息會係其他group見到<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.discuss.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.discuss.com.hk&d=Cxq6fU51OcuVLB8gp8NaV%2B2wegjmRFMzjbv%2B285MJ7g%3D&h=9f65d5d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.discuss.com.hk</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.baby-kingdom.com/forum.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.baby-kingdom.com%2Fforum.php&d=Cxq6fU51OcuVLB8gp8NaV%2B2wegjmRFMzjbv%2B285MJ7g%3D&h=a981eb8a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.baby-kingdom.com/forum.php</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香討/babykingdom，全世界都知，我地嘅大本營，消息最快、最新、最準確</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">最後，祝大家早日爆機！</span></span>"},{"pid":"f1612f09f38fa3a4ffa0f2e9838557251794ea90","tid":1281471,"uid":187796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T09:50:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6bae29576ab0d62d1dfb240d875249e50ac804c2","tid":1281471,"uid":187796,"like":0,"dislike":